152
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:44,770
Jinzhao.

153
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:47,810
The goods have gone wrong.

154
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:48,860
Go find Mr. Chen Quickly

155
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:53,860
I told you

156
