277
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,290
After much thought,

278
00:16:53,650 --> 00:16:54,810
I think Shanxi

279
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:57,290
might be the best place for me.

280
00:16:58,290 --> 00:16:59,410
You don't mean...

281
00:17:01,530 --> 00:17:03,500
I plan to comb my hair up*
[Women who refuse marriage and choose to remain single]

282
00:17:03,930 --> 00:17:04,930
and move to Shanxi

283
00:17:05,650 --> 00:17:06,620
