284
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,250
Because of your mother.

285
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:11,690
Yes.

286
00:17:13,010 --> 00:17:13,860
Indeed,

287
00:17:14,650 --> 00:17:15,930
