290
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:21,490
The sages teach:

291
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:23,060
In marriage,

292
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:24,580
harmony is the most precious.

293
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:26,410
Marriage only makes sense

294
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:27,860
if it benefits both people.

295
00:17:27,930 --> 00:17:28,930
That's the right way.

296
00:17:30,380 --> 00:17:31,780
But when I think about myself,

297
00:17:32,210 --> 00:17:33,580
I truly can't see

298
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:35,140
any benefit

299
00:17:35,340 --> 00:17:36,380
marriage would bring me.

300
00:17:37,490 --> 00:17:38,300
So

301
00:17:38,490 --> 00:17:39,540
I've decided not

302
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:40,690
to take that risk.

303
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:48,060
I'm sorry

304
00:17:49,450 --> 00:17:50,650
I shouldn't have

305
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:52,210
said all this to you.

306
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:54,780
What you've said

307
00:17:55,930 --> 00:17:57,140
never crossed my mind.

308
00:17:57,620 --> 00:17:59,100
I don't know how to respond.

309
00:18:00,250 --> 00:18:01,340
But you're right.

310
00:18:01,970 --> 00:18:02,780
Something

311
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:04,060
is only worth doing

312
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,170
if it brings benefit.

313
00:18:07,650 --> 00:18:08,410
So...

314
00:18:10,410 --> 00:18:11,730
When will you go to Shanxi?

315
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,210
I haven't decided yet.

316
00:18:15,970 --> 00:18:16,730
But

317
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:18,340
if I do go,

318
00:18:19,010 --> 00:18:20,100
I'll wait until

319
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,540
my grandmother passes away.

320
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,340
Miss! Mr. Chen!

321
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:29,170
Mr. Chen! Miss!

322
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,620
Mr. Chen! Jinzhao!

323
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:31,730
Mr. Chen! Miss!
Jinzhao!

324
00:18:32,450 --> 00:18:33,340
Mr. Chen! Miss!
Mr. Chen!

325
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:35,100
Jinzhao!

326
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,410
Miss! Jinzhao!

327
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:36,900
What should we do?
Mr. Chen!

328
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:38,380
How could this happen

329
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,650
in such a short time?

330
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:42,140
Look!

331
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:43,650
Smoke over there!

332
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:44,730
Hurry over!
Let's go!

333
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:46,540
Come on!

334
00:18:58,340 --> 00:18:59,410
Mr. Chen.

335
00:18:59,650 --> 00:19:00,690
Is he dead?

336
00:19:02,410 --> 00:19:03,580
He wasn't as lucky as us.

337
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,060
We had leaves to cushion our fall.

338
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:06,970
He hit the rocks.

339
00:19:07,450 --> 00:19:08,340
It killed him.

340
00:19:09,780 --> 00:19:10,450
Mr. Chen.

341
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:11,900
Look inside his shirt.

342
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:12,930
Is there something there?

343
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:16,930
Silver notes.

344
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:19,450
Xinlong Bank, Guiyang Branch.

345
00:19:22,410 --> 00:19:23,410
There's a letter too.

346
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:27,170
These bandits

347
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:28,690
were definitely planning this all along.

348
00:19:29,450 --> 00:19:30,140
They must have targeted your family

349
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:31,580
from the very start.

350
00:19:32,820 --> 00:19:33,730
May I see it?

351
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:40,140
[Miss,]

352
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:42,250
[this is a new prescription from Divine Healer Xiao]

353
00:19:50,210 --> 00:19:50,900
Miss Gu?

354
00:19:53,970 --> 00:19:54,580
Jinzhao?

355
00:19:58,340 --> 00:20:00,450
This handwriting is exactly the same

356
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,060
as the Divine Healer Xiao

357
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:03,210
who treated my mother.

358
00:20:03,730 --> 00:20:04,540
You mean...

359
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,730
The physician Ye Xian hired for you?

360
00:20:07,170 --> 00:20:07,730
Yes.

361
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:10,170
His name is Xiaoyou.

362
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:11,690
Ye Xian's master.

363
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:13,580
Xiaoyou.

364
00:20:14,170 --> 00:20:15,380
What does he look like?

365
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:17,780
High nose, narrow eyes,

366
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:18,970
thin lips like a blade.

367
00:20:20,210 --> 00:20:20,690
That's right.

368
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:22,250
He grows a lump

369
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:24,690
on his left earlobe.

370
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:26,820
It's true.

371
00:20:28,450 --> 00:20:29,450
No wonder I couldn't find him
no matter how hard I looked.

372
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:32,210
I was wondering

373
00:20:32,210 --> 00:20:33,540
how to protect the Marquis of Changxing's mansion.

374
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:34,930
I was blind to it.

375
00:20:35,490 --> 00:20:36,650
You've been looking for him?

376
00:20:37,580 --> 00:20:38,340
Yes.

377
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:41,340
Xiaoyou is not his real name.

378
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:43,450
His real name is Xiao Qishan.

379
00:20:43,930 --> 00:20:45,540
He was the top advisor

380
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:47,210
to the late Prince Chengqing.

381
00:20:47,930 --> 00:20:48,580
But

382
00:20:49,300 --> 00:20:50,650
He's Ye Xian's master.

383
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,380
Does that mean Ye Xian,

384
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:53,970
and the entire Marquis of Changxing's mansion,

385
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,780
are all involved?

386
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:58,780
Yes.

387
00:21:03,540 --> 00:21:04,210
[Jinzhao!]
[Mr. Chen!]

388
00:21:05,650 --> 00:21:06,490
Besides the Ji Mansion staff,
all available constables and guards

389
00:21:07,250 --> 00:21:08,650
from Tongzhou government

390
00:21:08,900 --> 00:21:09,690
have gone out to search.

391
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,580
[Mrs. Ji also paid handsomely]
[to hire escorts from]

392
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:13,650
[Weiyuan and Fuyuan Escort Agencies]

393
00:21:13,650 --> 00:21:14,540
[to help with the search.]

394
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:16,170
[We didn't waste any time.]

395
00:21:18,170 --> 00:21:19,210
All the bandits have been caught.

396
00:21:19,690 --> 00:21:20,450
They confessed:

397
00:21:20,930 --> 00:21:22,140
only two leaders

398
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,340
are from the southwest.

399
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:24,490
The one who kidnapped Miss Gu
is one of them.

400
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:26,900
These two leaders

401
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:28,730
take direct orders from Xiao.

402
00:21:29,250 --> 00:21:30,010
The rest

403
00:21:30,580 --> 00:21:31,380
are just bandits
recruited along the way.

404
00:21:33,780 --> 00:21:34,730
Did they confess
where these weapons

405
00:21:36,010 --> 00:21:37,170
are being delivered?

406
00:21:37,970 --> 00:21:38,650
To a manor

407
00:21:38,650 --> 00:21:39,970
outside the capital belonging to Prince Glorian.

408
00:21:41,210 --> 00:21:42,210
Just as I thought.

409
00:21:42,780 --> 00:21:43,340
Mr. Chen!

410
00:21:43,900 --> 00:21:45,170
Should we keep quiet

411
00:21:45,170 --> 00:21:47,100
about Xiao Qishan hiding in the Marquis' mansion?

412
00:21:47,930 --> 00:21:49,690
Should we not talk about it for now

413
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:53,100
I spoke out of turn.

414
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:55,780
By the way, you said

415
00:21:56,340 --> 00:21:57,780
only two leaders

416
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,340
are their own men.

417
00:21:59,930 --> 00:22:02,060
The rest are hired hands.

418
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:04,780
Then gather another group

419
00:22:05,300 --> 00:22:06,620
and deliver these weapons

420
00:22:06,620 --> 00:22:07,780
secretly

421
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,540
to Prince Glorian's manor.

422
00:22:09,930 --> 00:22:11,300
Pretend nothing happened.

423
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:12,620
Can you do that?

424
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,170
It should be done.

425
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:16,930
I can handle it discreetly.

426
00:22:17,730 --> 00:22:18,730
I'll go arrange it now.

427
00:22:21,540 --> 00:22:22,010
Good

428
00:22:23,250 --> 00:22:24,010
Why are you here?

429
00:22:26,450 --> 00:22:27,450
Your ankle just healed.

430
00:22:27,650 --> 00:22:28,450
Walk slowly

431
00:22:29,210 --> 00:22:29,930
I know

432
00:22:31,060 --> 00:22:31,690
Mr. Chen,

433
00:22:31,730 --> 00:22:32,730
I don't think Ye Xian

434
00:22:32,930 --> 00:22:34,410
knows about Xiaoyou's true identity.

435
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:36,010
If he knew,

436
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:37,300
he would have
hidden him away.

437
00:22:38,490 --> 00:22:39,540
He'd never let him

438
00:22:39,780 --> 00:22:41,450
treat my mother openly.

439
00:22:42,170 --> 00:22:43,780
He must be kept in the dark.

440
00:22:46,210 --> 00:22:47,490
That makes sense,

441
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:48,690
but

442
00:22:49,060 --> 00:22:49,930
do you have proof?

443
00:22:51,250 --> 00:22:52,900
Even if Ye Xian doesn't know,

444
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:54,300
what about Lord Changxing?

445
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,100
Is he also clueless?

446
00:23:01,170 --> 00:23:02,250
To be honest,

447
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:04,100
I don't believe

448
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:05,540
that

449
00:23:05,540 --> 00:23:06,900
Lord Changxing would rebel.

450
00:23:07,250 --> 00:23:07,930
Because

451
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:09,930
he and the late Prince Chengqing

452
00:23:09,930 --> 00:23:11,100
are sworn enemies.

453
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:11,970
Years ago,

454
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:13,900
when Prince Chengqing's rebellion failed,

455
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:15,140
Lord Changxing

456
00:23:15,450 --> 00:23:16,620
beheaded him

457
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:17,900
on the battlefield.

458
00:23:19,970 --> 00:23:21,140
Is that true?

459
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:24,580
So

460
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:26,340
belief alone

461
00:23:26,340 --> 00:23:27,580
isn't enough.

462
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:29,780
Xiao Qishan has been sheltered

463
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:30,690
by Lord Changxing's for years,

464
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:32,010
and he is Ye Xian's master.

465
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:33,490
On these two counts,

466
00:23:33,930 --> 00:23:34,730
Lord Changxing
can't escape blame.

467
00:23:38,060 --> 00:23:38,580
Then...

468
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:41,650
do you have a way to save them?

469
00:23:48,060 --> 00:23:49,210
I have no way.

470
00:23:53,340 --> 00:23:55,060
I know you want to help Ye Xian,

471
00:23:55,380 --> 00:23:57,490
but this is of grave importance.

472
00:23:58,250 --> 00:23:58,970
You

473
00:23:59,690 --> 00:24:00,340
me,

474
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:01,820
the Ji family,
the Chen family—

475
00:24:02,690 --> 00:24:03,820
if we get caught up in this,

476
00:24:04,170 --> 00:24:05,140
one wrong move

477
00:24:05,860 --> 00:24:07,100
and we'll all be destroyed.

478
00:24:07,690 --> 00:24:08,490
Do you understand?

479
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:11,170
I understand.

480
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:14,860
Mr. Chen, we're ready to leave.

481
00:24:17,010 --> 00:24:17,540
Let's go.

482
00:24:18,060 --> 00:24:18,620
Then you

483
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:19,900
go back early too.

484
00:24:21,210 --> 00:24:22,210
Aren't you entering the city?

485
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:24,490
I must return to the capital.

486
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:30,490
Jinzhao.
Let's go back too.

487
00:24:32,410 --> 00:24:33,250
I'm not going back,

488
00:24:34,380 --> 00:24:35,010
Jinrong.
I have something urgent

489
00:24:36,060 --> 00:24:37,210
in the capital.

490
00:24:37,410 --> 00:24:38,300
Lend me two horses.

491
00:24:38,930 --> 00:24:39,860
Cover for me

492
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:41,250
with Grandmother,

493
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,540
please.

494
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,140
All right.

495
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:45,170
Then,
be careful on the road.

496
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:46,730
I will.

497
00:24:49,010 --> 00:24:49,490
Give it to me.

498
00:24:51,250 --> 00:24:51,690
Giddy up!
Miss,

499
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:53,970
are we betraying

500
00:24:53,970 --> 00:24:54,900
Mr. Chen

501
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:55,930
by sneaking back to the capital

502
00:24:56,060 --> 00:24:57,340
to warn the heir?

503
00:24:57,410 --> 00:24:57,930
No.

504
00:24:58,380 --> 00:24:59,490
As long as we don't get him,

505
00:24:59,780 --> 00:25:01,490
the Ji Mansion, or the Chen Mansion involved,

506
00:25:01,780 --> 00:25:02,650
it's fine.

507
00:25:03,340 --> 00:25:03,780
Giddy up!

508
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:09,410
Minister Ye,
take a seat.

509
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:17,060
I

510
00:25:17,340 --> 00:25:18,410
speak no idle words.

511
00:25:19,450 --> 00:25:20,970
Since Father fell ill,

512
00:25:21,170 --> 00:25:22,650
the palace has been in turmoil.

513
00:25:23,580 --> 00:25:25,490
All sorts of ghosts and gods appear.

514
00:25:26,010 --> 00:25:27,540
I've even heard repeated claims

515
00:25:28,450 --> 00:25:29,900
that I am too young

516
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:31,250
to rule the dynasty,

517
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:33,650
and Father should pass the throne to Prince Glorian.

518
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:35,860
Your Highness,

519
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:37,580
you trust me too much.

520
00:25:38,410 --> 00:25:40,620
If I cannot

521
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:41,300
tell loyal from traitorous,

522
00:25:42,650 --> 00:25:44,690
perhaps

523
00:25:44,690 --> 00:25:45,970
I truly am unfit to rule.

524
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:47,410
I know

525
00:25:47,650 --> 00:25:48,730
the whole of Lord Changxing's

526
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:49,970
are loyal subjects.

527
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:51,900
The words

528
00:25:52,060 --> 00:25:53,410
the Empress has said so many times,

529
00:25:53,730 --> 00:25:54,930
and so has Mr. Chen.

530
00:25:56,340 --> 00:25:57,490
Mr. Chen?

531
00:25:58,580 --> 00:25:59,340
Yeah.

532
00:26:00,170 --> 00:26:01,540
Mr. Chen said

533
00:26:01,970 --> 00:26:03,340
that among all military nobles,

534
00:26:04,010 --> 00:26:05,010
only Lord Changxing

535
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:06,380
would never betray Father.

536
00:26:07,970 --> 00:26:08,780
Once

537
00:26:09,100 --> 00:26:10,450
I could consult him,

538
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:11,970
Unfortunately,

539
00:26:11,970 --> 00:26:13,060
these days

540
00:26:13,250 --> 00:26:14,620
Mr. Chen is away on assignment.

541
00:26:15,170 --> 00:26:16,340
I had no choice

542
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:17,010
but to

543
00:26:17,010 --> 00:26:18,060
invite you here

544
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:18,930
in Frost's name.

545
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:22,690
I am at Your Highness's command.

546
00:26:23,060 --> 00:26:24,060
I shall not shrink from death.

547
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:41,100
Your Highness,

548
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:42,250
what is this?

549
00:26:42,730 --> 00:26:44,820
This is the map of the palace secret passages.

550
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,620
One end connects to the Eastern Palace,

551
00:26:47,060 --> 00:26:48,650
the other to the Imperial Garden.

552
00:26:49,410 --> 00:26:50,730
I tell you of this passage

553
00:26:51,210 --> 00:26:53,060
just in case of emergency.

554
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:54,210
If

555
00:26:54,210 --> 00:26:55,410
the crisis comes,

556
00:26:56,410 --> 00:26:57,010
I—

557
00:26:57,930 --> 00:26:58,970
If that day comes,

558
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,580
I will risk my life

559
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,410
to keep Your Highness safe.

560
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:21,860
My lord,

561
00:27:22,140 --> 00:27:23,340
a letter from Guard Li.

562
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,170
She's back.

563
00:27:46,930 --> 00:27:47,690
My lord.

564
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:17,140
You've grown even more rude

565
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:20,100
after months apart.

566
00:28:20,620 --> 00:28:21,210
How dare you

567
00:28:21,210 --> 00:28:22,410
drag me here

568
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:23,820
without

569
00:28:24,250 --> 00:28:24,970
even bowing!

570
00:28:26,930 --> 00:28:27,650
Qingpu,

571
00:28:28,690 --> 00:28:29,490
keep watch outside.
Yes, miss.

572
00:28:36,210 --> 00:28:37,340
I need to talk to you.

573
00:28:38,170 --> 00:28:39,970
It's about your master,

574
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:41,540
Divine Healer Xiao.

575
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,170
I don't believe you.

576
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:44,580
This is nonsense!

577
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:45,820
Many people
have identical handwriting.

578
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:48,140
You condemn him as Xiao Qishan

579
00:28:48,450 --> 00:28:49,930
and falsely accuse him of treason

580
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:51,170
over one note!

581
00:28:51,650 --> 00:28:52,410
I asked him to treat your mother

582
00:28:52,690 --> 00:28:53,380
for you,
to see your mother

583
00:28:54,860 --> 00:28:55,970
and this is how you repay me?

584
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:57,490
Ye Xian,

585
00:28:57,860 --> 00:28:58,540
Listen to me,.

586
00:28:58,540 --> 00:28:59,620
I don't want to hear a word!

587
00:29:05,450 --> 00:29:06,100
Miss,

588
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:07,900
we risked everything

589
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:09,210
to ride back through the night

590
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:10,650
to warn him,

591
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:11,930
and

592
00:29:11,930 --> 00:29:13,170
he's so ungrateful!

593
00:29:14,210 --> 00:29:15,100
He grew up

594
00:29:15,650 --> 00:29:17,340
with Divine Healer Xiao,

595
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:18,900
they're like father and son.

596
00:29:19,690 --> 00:29:20,970
It's normal

597
00:29:21,250 --> 00:29:22,140
he can't accept it.

598
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:24,380
But he's smart—

599
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,650
he'll know I'm not lying.

600
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,010
I won't talk nonsense.

601
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:34,210
My lord...

602
00:29:35,930 --> 00:29:36,820
Did you hear that?

603
00:29:37,250 --> 00:29:37,860
Yes.

604
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:38,930
My lord,

605
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:40,060
Do you believe it?

606
00:29:41,820 --> 00:29:42,860
I ask if you believe it.

607
00:29:43,250 --> 00:29:43,900
Did Master really lie to me

608
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:44,930
all these years?

609
00:29:45,450 --> 00:29:46,410
I don't know,

610
00:29:47,250 --> 00:29:48,170
but I don't think Miss Gu would lie.

611
00:29:48,730 --> 00:29:50,010
Miss Gu will not lie to me.

612
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:02,140
They all say

613
00:30:02,650 --> 00:30:04,620
Xiao Qishan

614
00:30:04,730 --> 00:30:05,860
incited Prince Chengqing

615
00:30:05,860 --> 00:30:07,900
to rebel.

616
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:09,620
I didn't believe it before,

617
00:30:10,490 --> 00:30:11,580
but now I see—

618
00:30:11,930 --> 00:30:14,380
right after the prince's defeat,

619
00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:15,860
he defected to the

620
00:30:16,060 --> 00:30:17,340
Lord Changxing's.

621
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,010
He's a crafty man.

622
00:30:22,690 --> 00:30:23,380
I was shocked

623
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,650
when

624
00:30:25,140 --> 00:30:26,450
I heard the news.

625
00:30:27,210 --> 00:30:27,780
But

626
00:30:28,060 --> 00:30:29,580
from what we've found,

627
00:30:29,860 --> 00:30:32,140
Prince Glorian and Xiao Qishan

628
00:30:32,410 --> 00:30:33,650
are colluding in treason,

629
00:30:34,650 --> 00:30:36,140
along with Lord Changxing.

630
00:30:39,690 --> 00:30:41,010
Master,

631
00:30:41,250 --> 00:30:42,250
what's your view

632
00:30:42,450 --> 00:30:43,340
on Lord Changxing's involvement?

633
00:30:44,340 --> 00:30:45,620
With Xiao Qishan there,

634
00:30:45,730 --> 00:30:48,100
Lord Changxing cannot be exonerated.

635
00:30:48,410 --> 00:30:50,060
Arrest him if we must.

636
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:58,690
Do you want to protect him?

637
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:01,210
No.

638
00:31:02,650 --> 00:31:04,100
But Lord Changxing

639
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:05,340
has won great battles

640
00:31:05,450 --> 00:31:06,820
and commands immense respect in the army.

641
00:31:07,210 --> 00:31:08,170
If he's gone,

642
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:09,580
who

643
00:31:09,580 --> 00:31:10,540
will defend Jiubian

644
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:12,450
if war breaks out?

645
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:16,690
Jiubian

646
00:31:16,820 --> 00:31:18,540
will not fight soon.

647
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:21,140
The treasury is full—

648
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:24,450
can we not train new soldiers?

649
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:27,970
Jiuheng,

650
00:31:28,690 --> 00:31:30,060
you're bright

651
00:31:30,140 --> 00:31:31,820
but inexperienced.

652
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:33,140
To improve,

653
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:33,970
you must think long-term.

654
00:31:34,340 --> 00:31:35,860
Take a long-term look

655
00:31:39,970 --> 00:31:40,490
Yes.

656
00:31:53,970 --> 00:31:54,580
Mr. Chen,

657
00:31:55,690 --> 00:31:56,580
as you expected,

658
00:31:57,820 --> 00:31:58,930
Miss Gu rode back to the capital

659
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:00,690
right after we left,

660
00:32:01,010 --> 00:32:01,970
and went straight

661
00:32:02,170 --> 00:32:03,250
to see Ye Xian.

662
00:32:09,490 --> 00:32:10,170
Ms. Jinzhao!

663
00:32:10,490 --> 00:32:11,580
You're back!

664
00:32:14,580 --> 00:32:15,860
Ever since

665
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:16,650
you and Mr. Jingrong
went to Tongzhou,

666
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:19,010
Lord Gu lost his post.

667
00:32:19,340 --> 00:32:20,100
He spends all his days
at taverns,

668
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:22,140
ignoring everything.

669
00:32:22,410 --> 00:32:23,580
Now Ms. Lan

670
00:32:23,690 --> 00:32:24,860
handles all household affairs.

671
00:32:28,540 --> 00:32:29,650
While you were gone,

672
00:32:30,060 --> 00:32:31,650
I had your courtyard

673
00:32:32,300 --> 00:32:33,970
and Jinrong's

674
00:32:34,170 --> 00:32:36,060
cleaned every day.

675
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:39,170
You must be exhausted from the journey.

676
00:32:39,450 --> 00:32:40,780
I've told the kitchen

677
00:32:40,970 --> 00:32:41,930
to make
longan and red date soup

678
00:32:43,140 --> 00:32:44,250
to nourish you.

679
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:46,380
Thank you.

680
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:48,540
If you have something to say,

681
00:32:48,780 --> 00:32:49,900
say it.

682
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:58,210
I've come to apologize, Jinzhao.

683
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:00,250
I've reflected

684
00:33:00,450 --> 00:33:01,650
these days—

685
00:33:02,100 --> 00:33:03,730
I was foolish and blind

686
00:33:03,970 --> 00:33:05,450
to right and wrong.

687
00:33:05,860 --> 00:33:07,170
It won't happen again.

688
00:33:08,250 --> 00:33:08,970
Please,

689
00:33:08,970 --> 00:33:10,170
please forgive me.

690
00:33:12,010 --> 00:33:12,730
I'll obey you

691
00:33:13,210 --> 00:33:14,690
from now on,

692
00:33:15,010 --> 00:33:16,490
whatever you command.

693
00:33:19,730 --> 00:33:20,820
That doesn't

694
00:33:21,250 --> 00:33:22,140
sound like you.

695
00:33:23,490 --> 00:33:24,210
Get up.

696
00:33:27,780 --> 00:33:28,620
What do you want?

697
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,820
JInzhao is such a cheerful person,

698
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:35,650
that

699
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:37,780
I'll just say it straight.

700
00:33:39,410 --> 00:33:40,410
I heard that

701
00:33:40,690 --> 00:33:42,300
before you left for Tongzhou,

702
00:33:42,540 --> 00:33:44,300
you signed a paper with Lord Gu

703
00:33:45,010 --> 00:33:46,540
saying he can't interfere

704
00:33:46,970 --> 00:33:48,250
in your or Jinrong's marriages.

705
00:33:48,620 --> 00:33:49,930
It's up to you.

706
00:33:50,730 --> 00:33:51,690
I also want to be like you

707
00:33:51,690 --> 00:33:52,780
and Jinrong

708
00:33:53,250 --> 00:33:54,010
in the future

709
00:33:54,300 --> 00:33:55,010
if Lord Gu uses my marriage

710
00:33:55,010 --> 00:33:56,410
for gain,

711
00:33:57,930 --> 00:33:59,860
please help me.

712
00:34:09,170 --> 00:34:10,260
You do not agree?

713
00:34:10,970 --> 00:34:12,530
I don't agree to make a deal with you.

714
00:34:13,610 --> 00:34:14,660
Because it is not necessary.

715
00:34:17,450 --> 00:34:18,380
And I don't need

716
00:34:18,490 --> 00:34:19,570
you listen to me in everything.

717
00:34:20,410 --> 00:34:21,450
Your marriage.

718
00:34:22,340 --> 00:34:23,380
I don't want to get involved.

719
00:34:28,610 --> 00:34:29,610
Looks like you

720
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:31,180
still won't forgive me.

721
00:34:34,380 --> 00:34:35,050
Whatever.

722
00:34:35,820 --> 00:34:36,700
It is useless to talk more.

723
00:34:37,410 --> 00:34:38,660
Time sees people's hearts.

724
00:35:14,010 --> 00:35:14,570
Miss,

725
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:16,490
do you think

726
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:17,900
she's telling the truth?

727
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,220
Whether it's true or not,

728
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,380
from what I know of her,

729
00:35:24,010 --> 00:35:25,090
she probably means it.

730
00:35:28,050 --> 00:35:29,570
Sometimes I feel sorry for her.

731
00:35:29,860 --> 00:35:31,050
She's pretty pathetic, too.

732
00:35:32,820 --> 00:35:33,820
Unlike me,

733
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:35,450
she has no grandmother to rely on.

734
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:38,740
Now

735
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,050
she only has herself.

736
00:35:50,010 --> 00:35:51,010
I wonder

737
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:53,660
how Ye Xian is.

738
00:36:08,180 --> 00:36:09,010
Greetings, Young Lord.

739
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:10,700
Is Mr. Xiao here?

740
00:36:11,220 --> 00:36:11,970
My lord,

741
00:36:12,820 --> 00:36:14,010
Mr. Xiao and Lord Changxing

742
00:36:14,220 --> 00:36:15,090
are in a meeting.

743
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:23,220
I bribed the night-soil collector

744
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:24,660
to sneak into the manor and check.

745
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:25,610
There are two full chests

746
00:36:25,610 --> 00:36:26,740
of sharpened swords and spears,

747
00:36:26,930 --> 00:36:27,570
plus smoke bombs—

748
00:36:28,490 --> 00:36:29,700
all military-standard.

749
00:36:32,570 --> 00:36:33,380
It appears

750
00:36:33,820 --> 00:36:35,970
Mr. Xiao was right in your speculation.

751
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:39,180
Prince Glorian harbors evil intentions.

752
00:36:39,530 --> 00:36:41,130
[He's plotting something big.]

753
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:42,050
[Yes.]

754
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,260
[Looks like I guessed correctly.]

755
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:02,260
[It is indeed the Young Lord.]

756
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:03,490
Now that you're here.
Just come in.

757
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:08,340
Is Father meeting with Mr. Xiao?

758
00:37:08,820 --> 00:37:09,530
Or else,

759
00:37:09,780 --> 00:37:10,860
I'll come back later.

760
00:37:11,900 --> 00:37:12,660
No need.

761
00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:14,930
You've grown up.

762
00:37:15,450 --> 00:37:16,220
The Marquis'

763
00:37:16,530 --> 00:37:17,930
will be yours one day.

764
00:37:19,410 --> 00:37:20,570
We are deliberating today.

765
00:37:21,450 --> 00:37:22,450
Come and listen too.

766
00:37:26,050 --> 00:37:26,740
Come in.

767
00:37:31,490 --> 00:37:33,380
How did you know

768
00:37:34,490 --> 00:37:35,660
Prince Glorian is buying weapons illegally?

769
00:37:35,970 --> 00:37:37,490
Actually, you don't know

770
00:37:37,860 --> 00:37:39,130
I've been ordering Mr. Xiao to secretly monitor

771
00:37:39,130 --> 00:37:41,130
Prince Glorian's Mansion.

772
00:37:46,450 --> 00:37:47,820
These days, Prince Glorian

773
00:37:48,090 --> 00:37:50,130
has been close to Yun Tao, Commander of the North City Garrison,

774
00:37:50,570 --> 00:37:52,090
and Lv Ming,

775
00:37:52,090 --> 00:37:53,010
Chief of the Left Jinwu Guard,

776
00:37:53,660 --> 00:37:54,410
Last month, he even gave

777
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:55,780
Commander Yun

778
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:56,930
two beauties from the Western Regions.

779
00:38:21,340 --> 00:38:22,780
That's too much to say.

780
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:24,820
No amount of water to drink will help.

781
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:27,300
I remember you

782
00:38:28,260 --> 00:38:29,450
are not very talkative before.

783
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:31,820
Before, I lived in the mountains.

784
00:38:32,700 --> 00:38:34,300
Apart from you,

785
00:38:34,660 --> 00:38:35,930
there were only monkeys.

786
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:37,610
Not much to say.

787
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:46,340
What are you staring at me like this?

788
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:49,130
You secretly helped my father to spy on

789
00:38:49,130 --> 00:38:50,260
Prince Glorian's mansion.

790
00:38:50,490 --> 00:38:51,410
Such a big thing.

791
00:38:52,220 --> 00:38:53,260
Why do you keep hiding it from me?

792
00:38:57,220 --> 00:38:58,970
Not intentionally to hide it from you.

793
00:39:00,490 --> 00:39:02,010
Just think you're still young.

794
00:39:02,450 --> 00:39:03,900
There's no need to tell you.

795
00:39:05,340 --> 00:39:06,180
Why are you looking for me
in such a hurry?

796
00:39:10,180 --> 00:39:10,970
Gu Jinzhao.

797
00:39:11,490 --> 00:39:13,130
She came back from Tongzhou.

798
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:14,970
I want to see her,

799
00:39:15,610 --> 00:39:16,860
but I don't want to go empty-handed

800
00:39:17,220 --> 00:39:18,130
or

801
00:39:18,130 --> 00:39:19,660
with some cheap gift.

802
00:39:21,130 --> 00:39:22,410
So,

803
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:24,660
is there anything

804
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:26,220
that can be handled.

805
00:39:27,970 --> 00:39:28,660
[What good things]

806
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:29,900
[can I have here?]

807
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:31,450
[I only have bows,]
[daggers,]

808
00:39:32,930 --> 00:39:33,820
[hidden weapons,]

809
00:39:33,970 --> 00:39:34,530
[and poison.]

810
00:39:36,050 --> 00:39:37,660
[This slingshot is a new one I made.]

811
00:39:37,930 --> 00:39:38,900
[Take it if you want it.]

812
00:39:41,970 --> 00:39:43,180
[I don't want this.]

813
00:39:45,260 --> 00:39:46,090
I remember the slingshot you

814
00:39:46,090 --> 00:39:47,260
gave me back in the day.

815
00:39:48,570 --> 00:39:49,860
Did I send you a slingshot?

816
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:51,410
Yeah.

817
00:39:52,410 --> 00:39:53,490
When I went back to the Capital that year.

818
00:39:53,970 --> 00:39:54,970
I've just been there for a day,

819
00:39:54,970 --> 00:39:56,660
and I wrote to ask you to come and pick me up.

820
00:39:58,090 --> 00:39:58,900
I waited from the first day of the new year to

821
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:00,010
the fifteenth day of the first lunar month.

822
00:40:02,050 --> 00:40:03,090
You're finally came.

823
00:40:08,260 --> 00:40:08,860
[Ye Xian.]

824
00:40:09,610 --> 00:40:10,490
[Master.]

825
00:40:17,010 --> 00:40:17,700
[What's wrong?]

826
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,260
[Why are you unhappy?]

827
00:40:20,340 --> 00:40:22,860
[Look at what Master gave you.]

828
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:27,260
[I don't want a slingshot, ]

829
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:28,340
[I want a bolt.]

830
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:30,180
[You're too young.]

831
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:32,700
[Master promises you,]

832
00:40:32,970 --> 00:40:34,050
[when you grow up]

833
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:35,860
[Master will give you crossbows.]

834
00:40:38,180 --> 00:40:39,130
[A word is made.]

835
00:40:39,490 --> 00:40:40,820
[A word is made.]

836
00:40:44,490 --> 00:40:45,780
[You have such a good memory.]

837
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,740
[I don't remember at all.]

838
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:50,570
[Take this slingshot.]

839
00:40:55,930 --> 00:40:56,570
Forget it.

840
00:40:58,050 --> 00:40:59,530
I'd better look for something else.

841
00:41:07,220 --> 00:41:08,180
Well.

842
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:09,970
He's acting strange today.

843
00:41:14,490 --> 00:41:15,260
My lord,

844
00:41:16,050 --> 00:41:17,180
I'm looking for Ms. Jinzhao.

845
00:41:30,050 --> 00:41:30,660
Well?

846
00:41:30,970 --> 00:41:31,860
You were right—

847
00:41:32,010 --> 00:41:33,010
someone is following us.

848
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:43,610
You're finally willing
to believe what I said.

849
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:46,930
Yes.

850
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:48,740
I'm afraid of being suspected,

851
00:41:49,180 --> 00:41:49,970
so I came under the pretense

852
00:41:49,970 --> 00:41:51,380
of returning Baopu.

853
00:41:52,700 --> 00:41:53,820
Is there a side gate?

854
00:41:53,970 --> 00:41:54,930
I want to see Chen Yanyun,

855
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:55,860
immediately.

856
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:57,300
There is a small door to
the north of our house

857
00:41:58,660 --> 00:41:59,700
direct access to the small alley.

858
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:00,700
Particularly concealed.

859
00:42:01,050 --> 00:42:02,050
I'll take you right now.

860
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:29,220
Mr. Xiao,

861
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,610
tell me in front of my father

862
00:42:31,090 --> 00:42:32,570
Prince Glorian is hiding weapons

863
00:42:33,050 --> 00:42:33,530
and colluding with

864
00:42:33,530 --> 00:42:35,180
Commander of the North City Garrison,

865
00:42:35,180 --> 00:42:35,970
and the Jinwu Guard.

866
00:42:36,700 --> 00:42:37,820
I think,

867
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:40,220
it seemed like he was helping my father

868
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:41,570
guard against his rebellion.

869
00:42:43,930 --> 00:42:45,530
I trust Jinzhao wouldn't lie.

870
00:42:46,050 --> 00:42:47,340
But in this way,

871
00:42:48,180 --> 00:42:49,300
Xiaoyou basically told my father

872
00:42:49,300 --> 00:42:50,490
everything.

873
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:53,740
This plot.

874
00:42:54,530 --> 00:42:55,930
I'm a little confused.

875
00:42:58,050 --> 00:42:58,930
Could it be

876
00:42:59,410 --> 00:43:01,220
Xiaoyou did not betray Lord Changxing?

877
00:43:01,930 --> 00:43:03,180
